deps.context: find_package(ffmpeg components avformat avcodec avutil swscale swresample)

libs.content:
find_library(opensl_library names opensles
    doc "the opensl library")

find_library(sdl2_core_library
  names sdl2
  hints
  $env{sdl2dir}
  path_suffixes lib64 lib
  paths
  /sw
  /opt/local
  /opt/csw
  /opt
)

find_library(sdl2main_library
      names sdl2main
      hints
      $env{sdl2dir}
      path_suffixes lib64 lib
      paths
      /sw
      /opt/local
      /opt/csw
      /opt
    )

find_library(pulseaudio_library
             names pulse
             doc "the pulseaudio library"
)

find_library(oss_library
             names ossaudio
             doc "optional oss library"
)

find_library(portaudio_library
             names portaudio
             doc "the portaudio library"
)

find_library(soundio_library
             names sndio
             doc "the soundio library"
)
find_program( ndk_ccache "${_ndk_ccache}" doc "the path to ccache binary")

deps.context: AC_INIT([curl], [-], [a suitable curl mailing list: https://curl.se/mail/])
